# --- ECS (Elastic Container Service) Permissions ---
AmazonECSFullAccess
AmazonECSTaskExecutionRolePolicy
AmazonECSServiceRolePolicy

# --- ECR (Elastic Container Registry) Permissions (if using private container images) ---
AmazonEC2ContainerRegistryFullAccess

# --- RDS (PostgreSQL) Permissions ---
AmazonRDSFullAccess
AmazonRDSDataFullAccess

# --- S3 (Bucket Access for Data Storage) Permissions ---
AmazonS3FullAccess

# --- CloudWatch (Logs and Monitoring) Permissions ---
CloudWatchFullAccess
CloudWatchLogsFullAccess

# --- EC2 (Networking, Security Groups, Elastic IPs for ECS Tasks) Permissions ---
AmazonEC2FullAccess

# --- IAM (Role & Policy Management) Permissions ---
IAMFullAccess

# --- VPC (Networking Configuration for ECS/RDS) Permissions ---
AmazonVPCFullAccess

# --- Additional Useful Permissions (Optional but Recommended) ---
AWSCloudFormationFullAccess       # If using CloudFormation or Terraform for automation
AWSStepFunctionsFullAccess        # For orchestration workflows (optional)
AWSKeyManagementServicePowerUser  # If using KMS for S3 or RDS encryption
